**일시:** ██/██/████
**실험 대상:** Two (2) Litres of █████-brand paint primer

//절차:// 250 ml of SCP-447-2 was mixed thoroughly into the paint primer.

//결과:// The primer took on a green hue, and started to smell minty. The resulting paint was approximately 200% more opaque when compared to a different can of primer.

//주석:// This would be marketed in home improvement stores, but the chances of a dead body coming into contact with painted surfaces is too high, plus the smell of mint is overpowering when a whole room is painted with the primer.

